    "body": "So with bundler 1.10.0, and when that pull request is merged, it will be possible to directly install the grpc gem from git, even without grpc installed on the system, using the following:\n\n```\ngem 'grpc', :git => 'https://github.com/grpc/grpc.git', submodules: true, glob: 'src/ruby/*.gemspec'\n```\n"
